This document provides the complete Software Requirements Specifications (SRS) for a Restaurant Management System (namely RMS) 
that is meant to control the functioning of the activities of the restaurant in an organised manner. 
The restaurant Management system is a software which will be used to computerize the activities of the restaurant 
such as an online order request, Computerised bill generation, Employee and customer registration, Inventory, Employee payroll, 
Employee attendance and Employee grievance registration.  In the following sections, we specify the purpose of this document, 
its intended audience, and all sources used in the production of this document 

The attached files are Restaurant Management System developed using Visual Studio 2017 
